ight=\"343\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/b/bb/Strikeforce_Young_Guns_poster.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"270\" data-file-height=\"370\" /></a></span><div class=\"infobox-caption\">The poster for Strikeforce: Young Guns</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"infobox-label\" style=\"white-space: nowrap; width=33%\">Promotion</th><td class=\"infobox-data\"><a href=\"/wiki/Strikeforce_(mixed_martial_arts)\" title=\"Strikeforce (mixed martial arts)\">Strikeforce</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"infobox-label\" style=\"white-space: nowrap; width=33%\">Date</th><td class=\"infobox-data\">February 10, 2007</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"infobox-label\" style=\"white-space: nowrap; width=33%\">Venue</th><td class=\"infobox-data\"><a href=\"/wiki/San_Jose_Civic_Auditorium\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"San Jose Civic Auditorium\">San Jose Civic Auditorium</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"infobox-label\" style=\"white-space: nowrap; width=33%\">City</th><td class=\"infobox-data\"><a href=\"/wiki/San_Jose,_California\" title=\"San Jose, California\">San Jose, California</a>, United States</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"infobox-label\" style=\"white-space: nowrap; width=33%\">Attendance</th><td class=\"infobox-data\">3,169</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-header\" style=\"background:lightgrey;color:inherit; text-decoration:none;\">Event chronology</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-full-data\"><span></span>\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align: center; line-height: 1.4em; vertical-align: top\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33%; text-align: center; padding: 0.2em 0.1em 0.2em 0\"><a href=\"/wiki/Strikeforce:_Triple_Threat\" title=\"Strikeforce: Triple Threat\">Strikeforce: Triple Threat</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33%; text-align: center; padding: 0.2em 0.1em 0.2em 0.1em; font-weight: bold;\">Strikeforce: Young Guns\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33%; text-align: cent